description:
AJKB-02 EMBROIDERED NET 3 PCS

By Pcs: 3 Pcs Peshwas: Net Trouser: Silk Dupatta: Net Color: Green

Draped in the emerald richness of a royal garden, this bottle green ensemble captures a timeless elegance. The embroidered Peshwas, a true symbol of regalia, is adorned with gold zariwork winding gracefully among sparkling golden sequins like morning dewdrops. Paired with a magenta embroidered dupatta that mirrors a twilight sky above the garden, this regal creation resonates with an elegance that lingers through the night.
DESIGN DETAILS:

Embroidered front bodice on net
Embroidered back bodice on net
1.25 meterembroidered border for bodice hem on net
Embroidered 16 Kalis with 5 meterembroidered ghera border on net
Pair of embroidered sleeves on net
2.5 meter embroidered dupatta with 4-side border on net
1.5 meter wide-width silk for trouser
